---
import BlogArticleLayout from '../../layouts/BlogArticleLayout.astro';
---

<BlogArticleLayout
  title="Able Family Dental Launches New Website | Clinic News"
  description="Able Family Dental has launched a new website to make it easier for patients to find information, request appointments, and connect with the care they need."
  category="Clinic News"
  categoryStyle="blue"
  headline="We've Launched a New Website to Better Serve Our Patients"
  readTime="3 min read"
  date="June 2025"
  dateIso="2025-06-01"
  heroImage="/images/blog/new-website-launch.png"
  heroImageAlt="Person browsing the new Able Family Dental website on a laptop"
  currentSlug="new-website-launch"
>

  <div class="space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text)]">

    <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
      We are pleased to share that Able Family Dental has launched a new website, designed to make it easier for patients, both new and returning, to find the information they need and connect with our team.
    </p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Why we built a new site</h2>
      <p>
        Our goal was straightforward: make it simpler for patients to understand what we offer, learn what to expect from a visit, and reach us when they need care. The previous site had served us well, but as our services grew and patient needs evolved, we felt it was time for an update that better reflected how we work and what we stand for.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        We wanted a site that works well on any device, whether you are on a phone at home, a tablet in the waiting room, or a desktop at work, and gives you clear, straightforward information without unnecessary friction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">What's new for patients</h2>

      <div class="space-y-5 mt-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base"><span class="text-brand-accent">Online appointment requests</span></p>
          <p class="mt-1.5">You can now submit an appointment request directly through the site at any time. No need to call during office hours. Our team will follow up to confirm your date and time.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base"><span class="text-brand-accent">Expanded service information</span></p>
          <p class="mt-1.5">Each of our services now has its own dedicated page with plain-language explanations of what the treatment involves, who it may be appropriate for, and what to expect before and after your appointment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base"><span class="text-brand-accent">New patient resources</span></p>
          <p class="mt-1.5">We have added a dedicated section for new patients that covers what to bring to your first visit, how our office handles insurance and payment, and answers to common questions about getting started with a new dental provider.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base"><span class="text-brand-accent">Patient education blog</span></p>
          <p class="mt-1.5">Our blog is home to articles on oral health topics written by our team, covering preventive care, what to expect from common treatments, and general guidance for patients of all ages. New articles will be added regularly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Built with accessibility in mind</h2>
      <p>
        The new site was built to be accessible to patients regardless of how they browse. Text is sized for readability, navigation is keyboard-accessible, and the layout adapts clearly to smaller screens. We have also taken care to ensure that contact information, including our phone number, hours, and address, is easy to find on every page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-border-soft)] pt-8">
      <p>
        We hope the new site makes it easier to get the information you need and stay connected with our clinic. If you have questions or would like to request an appointment, please reach out. We are always happy to hear from you.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        Call us at <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-hover)] transition-colors">403.327.7202</a> or request an appointment online.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

</BlogArticleLayout>
